we’re financially solid, we don’t have so much\h
free cash flow, so we’d have to take on debt.\h\h

44
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:29,200
Instead, I think we should focus\h
on our North American presence,\h\h

45
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:34,640
where we’re already in a strong market\h
position and the competition is less intense.\h

46
